flowchart LR
    INPUT[用户输入] --> PARSE[意图解析]
    PARSE --> HOME[自己做链路]
    PARSE --> OUT[出去吃链路]
    HOME --> XHS_RECIPE[小红书菜谱检索]
    OUT --> MAP[高德地图 POI 搜索]
    OUT --> XHS_STORE[小红书探店笔记检索]
    XHS_RECIPE --> MERGE[LLM 结构化融合]
    MAP --> MERGE
    XHS_STORE --> MERGE
    MERGE --> GUARD[Graph-RAG 健康校验]
    GUARD --> UI[前端卡片展示]
    UI --> PDF[ReportLab 导出 PDF]
    PDF --> MEM[Milvus 足迹写入]
